        <strong><u>What We Are</u></strong>
        <p>Doki Doki Modding Central is an all-encompassing fan modification emporium for modifying Doki Doki Literature Club! by Team Salvato. Made by a handful of individuals with years of experience in the DDLC modding scene, this website is made in hopes to provide a space for the consumption, exploration, critique, and creation of modifications for the franchise. This initiative is cultivated by providing a repository of mods, new and republished, regardless of petty internet drama or stigma. Alongside this, we wish to provide the resources necessary to generate new content for the franchise and give a foot in the door for new entrants into game creation. The implementation of a forum for discussion of modifications hopes to achieve a ground of active communication and attributing to the betterment of mod creation and story-telling, meanwhile giving a place for fans to discuss amongst themselves and provide crucial feedback on works that the authors can partake in.</p>
